{"owner": "lexolab", "repo": "alejandro-alvarado-landing", "path": "index.html", "message": "Add index.html", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>Alejandro Alvarado Rojas | Clases de Charango e Instrumentos Andinos</title>\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@500;700;800&family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --gold: #d4a437;\n      --gold-soft: #f1cf72;\n      --cream: #f7f1e3;\n      --brown: #1a0f0a;\n      --brown-soft: #2b1810;\n      --red: #9c2f1f;\n      --green: #476c38;\n      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);\n    }\n\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n      color: white;\n      background:\n        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(212, 164, 55, 0.18), transparent 30%),\n        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(156, 47, 31, 0.28), transparent 45%),\n        linear-gradient(160deg, #120905 0%, #1b100b 45%, #0f0906 100%);\n      min-height: 100vh;\n    }\n\n    body::before {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: fixed;\n      inset: 0;\n      pointer-events: none;\n      opacity: 0.08;\n      background-image:\n        linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 48%, var(--gold) 49%, var(--gold) 51%, transparent 52%),\n        linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 48%, var(--gold) 49%, var(--gold) 51%, transparent 52%);\n      background-size: 36px 36px;\n      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, rgba(0,0,0,0.2));\n    }\n\n    .wrap {\n      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .hero {\n      padding: 32px 0 56px;\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .topbar {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 16px;\n      margin-bottom: 36px;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 207, 114, 0.22);\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      border-radius: 18px;\n      padding: 14px 18px;\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n    }\n\n    .brand {\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      font-size: 1.1rem;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .badge {\n      padding: 10px 16px;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--red));\n      font-size: 0.85rem;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      letter-spacing: 0.8px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .hero-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;\n      gap: 34px;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n\n    .eyebrow {\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 3px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 0.82rem;\n      margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.9rem);\n      line-height: 0.95;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      text-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);\n    }\n\n    .highlight {\n      color: var(--gold);\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .lead {\n      margin: 22px 0 26px;\n      font-size: 1.08rem;\n      line-height: 1.75;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);\n      max-width: 640px;\n    }\n\n    .cta-row {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 14px;\n      margin-bottom: 26px;\n    }\n\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 10px;\n      padding: 14px 24px;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;\n    }\n\n    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }\n\n    .btn-primary {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #b97b16);\n      color: #1b1007;\n      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(212, 164, 55, 0.3);\n    }\n\n    .btn-secondary {\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);\n      color: white;\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n    }\n\n    .stats {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));\n      gap: 14px;\n    }\n\n    .stat {\n      border-radius: 18px;\n      padding: 18px;\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n    }\n\n    .stat strong {\n      display: block;\n      font-size: 1.8rem;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-card {\n      position: relative;\n      border-radius: 28px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      min-height: 620px;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 207, 114, 0.24);\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n      isolation: isolate;\n      background: #120905;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-card::after {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: auto 0 0 0;\n      height: 10px;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1f7a34, #d0a62a, #a92f21);\n      z-index: 3;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-image {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 100%;\n      min-height: 620px;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-overlay {\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: auto 0 0 0;\n      padding: 28px;\n      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(13, 8, 6, 0.95), rgba(13, 8, 6, 0.15));\n      z-index: 2;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-overlay h2 {\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      font-size: 2rem;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .portrait-overlay p {\n      margin: 0;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    section {\n      padding: 22px 0 34px;\n    }\n\n    .section-title {\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-bottom: 28px;\n    }\n\n    .section-title span {\n      display: inline-block;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      letter-spacing: 3px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-size: 0.82rem;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .section-title h3 {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .courses {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));\n      gap: 18px;\n    }\n\n    .course {\n      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.07), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\n      border-radius: 22px;\n      padding: 24px;\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .course::before {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0;\n      left: 0;\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 4px;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--gold), var(--red));\n    }\n\n    .course h4 {\n      margin: 0 0 10px;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      font-size: 1.15rem;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .course p {\n      margin: 0;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\n      line-height: 1.7;\n    }\n\n    .info-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 22px;\n      margin-top: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .panel {\n      border-radius: 24px;\n      padding: 28px;\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 207, 114, 0.16);\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n    }\n\n    .panel h4 {\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-size: 1.35rem;\n    }\n\n    .list {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n      display: grid;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .list li {\n      padding-left: 18px;\n      position: relative;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\n      line-height: 1.65;\n    }\n\n    .list li::before {\n      content: '\u2726';\n      position: absolute;\n      left: 0;\n      color: var(--gold);\n    }\n\n    .contact-box {\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 36px 28px;\n      border-radius: 28px;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(71,108,56,0.22), rgba(156,47,31,0.18), rgba(212,164,55,0.16));\n      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 207, 114, 0.16);\n      box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n    }\n\n    .contact-box h3 {\n      margin: 0 0 12px;\n      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);\n      color: var(--gold-soft);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    .contact-box p {\n      max-width: 760px;\n      margin: 0 auto 18px;\n      line-height: 1.75;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      padding: 28px 0 42px;\n      text-align: center;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 980px) {\n      .hero-grid,\n      .info-grid,\n      .courses {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n\n      .portrait-card { min-height: 520px; }\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 720px) {\n      .topbar {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: flex-start;\n      }\n\n      .stats {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n\n      .hero {\n        padding-top: 20px;\n      }\n\n      h1 {\n        line-height: 1.02;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header class=\"hero\">\n    <div class=\"wrap\">\n      <div class=\"topbar\">\n        <div class=\"brand\">Alejandro Alvarado Rojas</div>\n        <div class=\"badge\">Clases de m\u00fasica andina</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"hero-grid\">\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"eyebrow\">Formaci\u00f3n folcl\u00f3rica con estilo moderno</div>\n          <h1>\n            Clases de <span class=\"highlight\">Charango</span>\n            e Instrumentos Andinos\n          </h1>\n          <p class=\"lead\">\n            Aprende de forma pr\u00e1ctica, din\u00e1mica y cultural con Alejandro Alvarado Rojas, charanguista dedicado a ense\u00f1ar con m\u00e9todos propios y did\u00e1cticos. Una propuesta musical pensada para ni\u00f1os, j\u00f3venes y adultos que quieren conectar con la riqueza del folclore andino.\n          </p>\n\n          <div class=\"cta-row\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#cursos\">Ver cursos</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#contacto\">Pedir informaci\u00f3n</a>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"stats\">\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <strong>6</strong>\n              Instrumentos disponibles\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <strong>100%</strong>\n              Enfoque pr\u00e1ctico y did\u00e1ctico\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <strong>Folclore</strong>\n              Tradici\u00f3n andina con imagen moderna\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"portrait-card\">\n          <img class=\"portrait-image\" src=\"alejandro-charango-hero.jpg\" alt=\"Alejandro Alvarado Rojas con charango\" />\n          <div class=\"portrait-overlay\">\n            <h2>Alejandro Alvarado Rojas</h2>\n            <p>Charanguista y formador musical, con una propuesta visual impactante y una ense\u00f1anza cercana para quienes desean aprender instrumentos andinos con identidad propia.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <section id=\"cursos\">\n    <div class=\"wrap\">\n      <div class=\"section-title\">\n        <span>Oferta musical</span>\n        <h3>Cursos disponibles</h3>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"courses\">\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Charango</h4>\n          <p>Aprende t\u00e9cnica, ritmo, melod\u00eda y acompa\u00f1amiento en uno de los instrumentos m\u00e1s emblem\u00e1ticos de la m\u00fasica andina.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Guitarra</h4>\n          <p>Clases para desarrollar acordes, punteos, acompa\u00f1amiento y seguridad musical desde lo b\u00e1sico hasta lo pr\u00e1ctico.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Mandolina</h4>\n          <p>Descubre un sonido brillante y vers\u00e1til, ideal para repertorios folcl\u00f3ricos y arreglos mel\u00f3dicos.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Flauta dulce</h4>\n          <p>Formaci\u00f3n musical accesible para iniciar lectura, digitaci\u00f3n y expresi\u00f3n sonora de manera sencilla.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Guitarra el\u00e9ctrica</h4>\n          <p>Explora t\u00e9cnica, ritmo y estilo con una ense\u00f1anza progresiva, adaptable al nivel del estudiante.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"course\">\n          <h4>Zampo\u00f1a</h4>\n          <p>Conecta con el sonido ancestral andino, aprendiendo respiraci\u00f3n, fraseo y sensibilidad interpretativa.</p>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <div class=\"wrap\">\n      <div class=\"section-title\">\n        <span>Metodolog\u00eda</span>\n        <h3>Aprendizaje garantizado</h3>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"info-grid\">\n        <div class=\"panel\">\n          <h4>\u00bfQu\u00e9 hace especial estas clases?</h4>\n          <ul class=\"list\">\n            <li>M\u00e9todos propios y did\u00e1cticos para avanzar con confianza.</li>\n            <li>Ense\u00f1anza pensada para distintos niveles y edades.</li>\n            <li>Enfoque pr\u00e1ctico, musical y cultural al mismo tiempo.</li>\n            <li>Ambiente inspirador con identidad folcl\u00f3rica andina.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"panel\">\n          <h4>Ideal para</h4>\n          <ul class=\"list\">\n            <li>Quienes quieren iniciar en la m\u00fasica andina.</li>\n            <li>Estudiantes que buscan t\u00e9cnica y repertorio.</li>\n            <li>Ni\u00f1os, j\u00f3venes y adultos con gusto por el folclore.</li>\n            <li>Personas que quieren aprender un instrumento con estilo y emoci\u00f3n.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"contacto\">\n    <div class=\"wrap\">\n      <div class=\"contact-box\">\n        <h3>Solicita informaci\u00f3n</h3>\n        <p>\n          Si quieres aprender charango e instrumentos andinos con una propuesta visual atractiva, moderna y con esencia folcl\u00f3rica, esta es tu oportunidad. Cont\u00e1ctate para conocer horarios, modalidad de clases y disponibilidad.\n        </p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0 auto 18px; max-width: 760px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); line-height: 1.8;\">\n          <strong>Tel:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+15716032645\" style=\"color: var(--gold-soft); text-decoration: none;\">(571) 603-2645</a><br>\n          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:alitoalvarado64@gmail.com\" style=\"color: var(--gold-soft); text-decoration: none;\">alitoalvarado64@gmail.com</a><br>\n          <strong>Ubicaci\u00f3n:</strong> Virginia, USA\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"cta-row\" style=\"justify-content:center; margin-bottom:0;\">\n          <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"mailto:alitoalvarado64@gmail.com\">Escribir por email</a>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"tel:+15716032645\">Llamar ahora</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer>\n    <div class=\"wrap\">Alejandro Alvarado Rojas \u00b7 Clases de Charango e Instrumentos Andinos</div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n", "branch": "main"}